data.description: Beautiful Open Floor plan single family home with 3 bedrooms, a den and 2 full baths in beautiful Copper Basin. Light and bright with a charming eat-in kitchen. This warm and inviting home has been well maintained by the owner and is move-in ready. You will love the new luxury vinyl plank flooring in the Den. The Primary bedroom is split from the others and features a large shower and walk-in closet. Private corner lot with a beautifully landscaped backyard is complete with easy care turf for the fur babies and a beautiful pergola and pavers to sit and enjoy with friends and family! Come see your new home today!
